dc_title_s: West Indies, Saint Vincent and Grenadines--Grenada--Trinidad and Tobago--Venezuela, Trinidad to Saint Vincent (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From U.S. and British Admiralty charts to 1995." Shipping list no.: 2004-2006-S. "Copyright 2004 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map No. 25400. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
